* Oh, chariots

31:58.280 --> 32:00.976
* If you're out there,
please swing low *

32:05.020 --> 32:08.581
* Tell I got here
at the right time *

32:08.620 --> 32:13.319
* And if I did,
it's probably the first time *

32:13.360 --> 32:18.662
* No second guesses
or secret signs *

32:18.700 --> 32:22.966
* Tell me I got here
at the right time. *

