OFFICER: Please remove
all metal objects

32:59.170 --> 33:01.775
and put them
in the bins.

33:01.810 --> 33:03.630
All laptops
must be separated

33:03.680 --> 33:06.148
out of your baggage
and taken out of their cases.

33:06.180 --> 33:08.740
All passengers...

33:08.780 --> 33:09.849
Can you raise your arms
for me, please, ma'am?

33:09.880 --> 33:12.644
WOMAN (over P.A.): At this time
I would like to ask

33:12.690 --> 33:14.715
all passengers
on flight 1893 to Orlando

33:14.760 --> 33:18.981
to please approach the gate
